Legs (
Fig. 4
) — Legs about half length of body. Setal formulae of leg segments as follows (specialized sensory setae such as solenidia, in parenthesis): coxae 2- 2 - 2 - 2; trochanters 1 - 1 - 2 - 1; femora 4 - 4 - 3 - 2, genua 5- 2 - 0 - 1; tibiae 5+1’ρ+1’ - 5+1’ρ - 5+1’ρ - 5+1’ρ; 13 (1ω) - 8 (1ω) - 7 (1ω) - 7 (1ω). Length of solenidia: ωI 10 (11), ωII 7 (6), ωIII 4 (4), ωIV 4 (4).
